==Catalan==
===Etymology===
Likely from {{bor|ca|pro|eissalot}} and its variants (e.g. {{m|pro|exaloc}}), from [[Massalia]]n {{der|ca|grc||*ἐξαλώτης}}, from {{m|grc|ἔξαλος|pos="out of the sea" → "wind from the southeast"}}. Traditionally thought to be a derivative of {{bor|ca|ar|شرق|tr=šarq|t=east}}.
